    "description": "i Cubed Systems, Inc. provides cloud-based mobile device management services under the CLOMO MDM name in Japan. Its solutions include CLOMO SecuredBrowser, a browser app that enables secure web browsing on smart devices; CLOMO SecuredContacts, a secure shared address book application; CLOMO SecuredDocs, a secure internal document sharing app; CLOMO SecuredMailer, a mail application that protects companies against the risk of information leakage; and CLOMO SecuredCalendar, a group calendar application that allows users to share schedule securely within the company. The company also provides operation support services. In addition, it offers Trend Vision One Mobile Security, a security solution that addresses both external threats targeting mobile devices and internal risks caused by misconfigurations; Deep Instinct, an anti-malware solution that incorporates deep learning into security measures; TeamViewer, a remote connection software; and Harmony Mobile, a security solution for mobile devices. It serves companies, educational, healthcare, and government agencies. The company was formerly known as i3 Systems,Inc. i Cubed Systems, Inc. was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Fukuoka City, Japan."
